@host = http://localhost:5000
@token = replace-with-jwt

GET {{host}}/health/live

### Active orders
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders/active?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Nearby drivers
GET {{host}}/api/v1/drivers/nearby?latitude=4.711&longitude=-74.0721&radiusMeters=5000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
